The paper deals with the problem of signal reconstruction from binary measurements, which is a common problem in information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.SP), and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper uses a convex optimization approach to solve the problem, which is a common technique in all of these sub-fields. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely candidates for this paper.
